{"tid":1726218,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國憲法：紀律良好的民兵隊伍，對於一個自由國家的安全實屬必要","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T17:12:11.000Z","uid":135891,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f9437834c8c453718e911f9e2926b361aa7b97","tid":1726218,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:11:08.000Z","msg":"美國憲法第二修正案<br />\n<br />\nA well regulated militia being necessary to the security of a free state, the right of the people to keep and bear arms shall not be infringed.<br />\n<br />\n紀律良好的民兵隊伍，對於一個自由國家的安全實屬必要；故人民持有和攜帶武器的權利，不得予以侵犯<br />\n<br />\n手足有反擊能力之後 我地就唔再係純粹嘅弱者 手足對維持香港嘅自由極之重要 所有嘅武器對維護香港自由亦屬必要<br />\n<br />\n但時刻謹記必須保持紀律優良 無論係民兵 軍隊 定紀律部隊都一樣 否則只會淪為黑警一樣被人民唾棄<br />\n做得好嘅野請 keep住<br />\n有做得唔好嘅地方請虛心聽手足意見<br />\n<br />\nBe humble Be water<br />\n只要團結 我們必勝"},{"pid":"0e55ffbfffa9d04b5e084b0f0df0a756f7527d01","tid":1726218,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"要時刻警醒"},{"pid":"b5fb3305c78dc01217d04740547ff44ed6b7d255","tid":1726218,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"嚴正呼籲，如果有所謂嘅白警，或者開始懼怕自己行為嘅警察，你有一件事可以做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0635e2e51bd480bdc525bbb07a0225fe664be4ca","tid":1726218,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"自律比內鬨分化好"},{"pid":"4db50d62d6300f3fb41fbdb389d40e038b1aac6c","tid":1726218,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"Agger 但勿再家醜外傳"},{"pid":"f0e1658d00d30bbccb39186834b3c6602e99fac2","tid":1726218,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"今次就當吸收經驗"},{"pid":"163d781eb89959d3be9771810cdc61d6e90d6734","tid":1726218,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy